      "localizedDescription": "A native iOS companion for your self-hosted GameVault server.\n\nTrack your game library \u2014 Now Playing, Completed, and Backlog \u2014 with full sync to your GameVault server. All your data stays on your own server; the app is just a native client.\n\nFeatures:\n\u2022 Dashboard with stats, hours played, platform & genre breakdown\n\u2022 Now Playing, Completed, and Backlog tabs\n\u2022 Search & add games from the RAWG.io database (500k+ titles)\n\u2022 Edit ratings, hours, reviews, and notes\n\u2022 Two-factor authentication (TOTP + email OTP)\n\u2022 Liquid Glass design for iOS 17+",
